  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK478">
<l>ākā ṟaḷaviṭṭi tāyiṉuṅ kēṭillai</l>
<l>pōkā ṟakalāk kaṭai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even though the income (of a king) be small, it will not cause his (ruin), if his outgoings be not larger than his income.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
